{"title":"Ah, Yeah, Purple Hayes Brakes are Back in a Limited Quantity","link":"https://bikerumor.com/purple-hayes-brakes-are-back-in-a-limited-quantity/","date":1741101888000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-hero.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"512\" alt=\"(Photos / Hayes Bicycle Group)\" /></p>\n<p>Purple seems to be reappearing everywhere lately with new color announcements and prototypes from <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pnw-purple-dropper-post-concept/\" target=\"_blank\">PNW</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-ultraviolet-purple-bike-parts/\" target=\"_blank\">WTC</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cane-creek-adds-purple-permanently-to-the-chroma-studio-collection/\" target=\"_blank\">Cane Creek</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/stinner-x-made-photo-stick-purple-rain/\" target=\"_blank\">Stinner</a>, and now Hayes. However, the Hayes Bicycle Group announced the <em>return</em> of the Purple Hayes Dominion A4 Brake, which first <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/a-purple-haze-hayes-brings-back-purple-ano-for-limited-edition-dominion-a4-disc-brakes/\" target=\"_blank\">appeared as a limited edition back in 2023</a>. It sold out quickly, but now a few sets are available again, but only for a limited time. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As the season kicked into gear, Hayes produced their annual batch of Purple Hayes for their pro athletes. They will be on each bike of their pro riders, but they produce a few extras every year. So, now you can have the same gear on your bike as your favorite pro.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-small-e1741022068824.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"905\" height=\"192\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-small-e1741022068824.webp\" alt=\"Purple Hayes Dominion A4 Brakes small\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-small-e1741022068824.webp 905w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-small-e1741022068824-297x63.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-small-e1741022068824-120x25.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-small-e1741022068824-768x163.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Hayes Bicycle Group)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Purple Hayes Dominion A4 Brakesets are now available for sale, and you can buy them by going to the following links: <a href=\"https://hayesbicycle.com/collections/dominion-a-series/products/purple-hayes-dominion-a4-brake-kit\" target=\"_blank\">USA</a>, or <a href=\"https://eu.hayesbicycle.com/collections/disc-brakes/products/purple-hayes-dominion-a4-brake-kit\" target=\"_blank\">Europe</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-lever-e1741021868576.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-lever-e1741021868576.webp\" alt=\"Purple Hayes Dominion A4 Brakes lever\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-lever-e1741021868576.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-lever-e1741021868576-297x186.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-lever-e1741021868576-120x75.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-lever-e1741021868576-768x480.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Purple-Hayes-Dominion-A4-Brakes-caliper-e1741021822701.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"764\" src=